data.description: SOLAR PANELS TO BE PAID OFF AT CLOSING!  Electric bill continues to goes down every month since activation.  As of 1/2024 it is under $90. Discover your new home nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac in the sought after community of Deep Creek.  This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom family home has been METICULOUSLY maintained!  Some of the recent updates include a NEW ROOF, Solar Panels (24) , New Skylight, 6 inch Gutters and Solar Roof Fan to keep the attic cool!!  New Pool Pump, Laundry Sink in garage, and New Exterior Impact windows and Doors, with shutters for front window and bathroom windows!!  There are many more updates!  Please see attached feature sheet for the whole impressive list!    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open concept design that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The spacious living room is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere for both family gatherings and entertaining friends.    The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar for casual dining. Cooking here is a pleasure, whether you're preparing family meals or hosting dinner parties.    The generous master suite is a true retreat, featuring a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with tiled walk-in shower. Two additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for guests, a home office, or a hobby room.    Step outside to the screened lanai, your private oasis for enjoying Florida's year-round sunshine. The backyard is a serene haven with lush landscaping, offering privacy and space for outdoor activities. It's the perfect spot to unwind with a cup of coffee in the morning or watch the sunset in the evening.    This home also offers the convenience of an attached two-car garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space.    Conveniently located near shopping centers, restaurants, golf courses, parks and schools, this home also offers quick access to I-75 for easy commuting to neighboring cities. Explore the beautiful Charlotte Harbor and Gulf of Mexico with ease, and enjoy outdoor activities at nearby parks, including Fishermen's Village and Ponce de Leon Park.    Don't miss the opportunity to make 2279 Bremen Ct your new home. Schedule your showing today and experience the Florida lifestyle you've been dreaming of!
